core":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"因為汽水係酸性，所以用鐵罐的話，會腐蝕。所以一般汽水罐都係用鋁做（俗稱鋁罐）。但是因為鋁材相對貴好多，所以鋁罐就有咁薄做咁薄，從而節省成本。所以睇落汽水罐較軟係因為鋁比鐵軟身，而且薄。<br />\n<br />\n而咖啡唔係碳酸飲料，唔係酸性，所以用鐵罐就可以。但是鐵的話因為韌性唔夠鋁罐咁好，所以需要做到罐壁相對較厚先可以維持到個鋼度。<br />\n<br />\n所以先覺得鐵罐較硬。"},{"pid":"2e3687950af147ebca84a9b6def962e3fa24f3a3","tid":1319404,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"各位記住千奇一定唔好買雀巢咖啡啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace1acaa0f9c01eb0eee14d64fce95e5d96845da","tid":1319404,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e68fcec04a9c5b84167ce3eef3573896e0ae3cb4","tid":1319404,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace1acaa0f9c01eb0eee14d64fce95e5d96845da","tid":1319404,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af50f004554fa76c52ec12fc5b73f420e943c6c3","tid":1319404,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"可樂果d又唔見佢咁硬<br />\n雀巢果個咖啡罐其實想點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d073b791cf2d7e538643cf669bf4bf9aa341e15","tid":1319404,"uid":31389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:26:40.000Z","msg":"塞入長襪,當流星錘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47da7d682e1ff93a3d42a65ebd6d409beb8f0929","tid":1319404,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}